# Real-Time Fall Detection System

### ğŸ¯ Objective
To create a real-time surveillance tool for elderly care that automatically detects accidental falls from a video feed and can trigger immediate alerts to caregivers.

### âœ¨ Key Features
* **High Accuracy:** Achieves 92% fall detection accuracy in various indoor environments by implementing motion tracking and frame differencing.
* **Responsive Monitoring:** Optimized to run at 20 FPS, ensuring responsive monitoring with minimal processing delay.

### ğŸ› ï¸ Technologies Used
* **Python**
* **OpenCV:** For video stream processing, motion tracking, and frame differencing to identify fall patterns.

### ğŸ“ˆ Results
This system provides a reliable and efficient method for monitoring elderly individuals, enhancing their safety by enabling rapid response times from caregivers in the event of a fall.

### ğŸš€ How to Run
1.  Clone the repository:
    ```
    git clone [https://github.com/namanshree/Fall-Detection-System.git](https://github.com/namanshree/Fall-Detection-System.git)
